**story**
Once apon a time in a forest, there lived a money who resided on a berry tree which was on the bank of a river. In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife. 
One day the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree, the kind hearted monkey offered him some fruis. The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits because he loved them.
So as days passed by, the crocodile and the monkey became good friends.
